A set of Vim configurations to use specially with Rails + Git

-- to set up the .vimrc file, use this command to create a symbolic link
ln -s vimrc ~/.vimrc

Needs:
- ctags               (>= 5.8)  http://ctags.sourceforge.net/

Have: (downloaded form http://www.vim.org/scripts/script.php?script_id={plugin_id})
----------------------------------------------------------------------
  plugin              version   id      [g]ithub/[b]itbucket
----------------------------------------------------------------------
- snipMate            (0.84)    [2540]  [g] msanders/snipmate.vim
- fugitive            (1.1)     [2975]  [g] tpope/vim-fugitive
- rails               (4.3)     [1567]  [g] tpope/vim-rails
- repeat              (1.0)     [2136]  [g] tpope/vim-repeat
- matchit             (1.13.2)  [ 39 ]
- ragtag              (2.0)     [1896]  [g] tpope/vim-ragtag
- surround            (1.9)     [1697]  [g] tpope/vim-surround
- fuf (FuzzyFinder)   (4.2.2)   [1984]  [b] ns9tks/vim-fuzzyfinder
